{
  "stem": "323.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's affected my life in different ways.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What has your mother taught you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rely on yourself.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] A lesson my brother has learned, as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, I felt without-- that's the only chance.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was my chance for survival, is that it's up to you, basically.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think it's something that I hope you teach your children, as well.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm hm And not so much that she's taught me, but just observing her life, that although I'm agnostic, I sometimes truly believe in the notion of angels, because she's had, in some respects, a very protected life, despite the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The fact that she survived and she's lived through some additional, very terrible experiences, has come out the other side.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I really think that she may, in fact, have a guardian angel at some point, looking out for her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Although it's exhibited in strange ways, by the fact that she survived the Holocaust but had to go through it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I believe that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, expensive sports, skiing and hiking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Unfortunately, with children it's hard to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the outdoors, yeah, definitely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I work at United Jewish Appeal, Federation of Jewish Philanthropies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I've been there for 10 years now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm in the program services department.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I direct a program that works with consultants who provide pro bono services to the agencies in New York who get funding from UJA Federation.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I also do some fund raising.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's very personally rewarding and meaningful to me to be there, one of the reasons I've been there for 10 years.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I enjoy it very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It really gives purpose to my life in many respects.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Partially, Jill's father was the kind of person that believed that one should work for nonprofit organizations and was more or less anti-establishment.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
